## ğŸ“ˆ Business Insights You Can Learn:

| Metric                            | What It Tells                                                       |
| --------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| âœ… **Signal Accuracy (e.g., 98%)** | Sensor is performing well and measuring close to expected.          |
| âš ï¸ **Noise Level (e.g., 8%)**     | Few sudden spikes show slight instability; needs filtering.         |
| âœ… **Latency (<1s)**               | Data is reaching system fast â€” good for real-time decisions.        |
| âœ… **Uptime (96.67%)**             | Sensor is mostly reliable, only small downtime.                     |
| âš ï¸ **Drift (\~0.5 Âµg/mÂ³)**        | Sensor shows a minor shift over time â€” recalibration may be needed. |
| âœ… **Response Time (avg 1.1s)**    | Acceptable for environment-sensitive devices like air purifiers.    |
| âœ… **Std Dev (1.2)**               | Low deviation = consistent performance.                             |
| âš ï¸ **Missing Data (5%)**          | Could impact long-term data trends â€” check network/power issues.    |

